Dietes bicolor irises, serenaded by the late afternoon sun.
</p>
<p class="jp">
<span class="title_jp">ディエテス属</span>
「ディエテス・バイカラー」。西日にやさしく照らされて。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Palos Verdes" /><category term="Flowers" /><category term="Golden Hour" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Dietes bicolor irises, serenaded by the late afternoon sun. ディエテス属 「ディエテス・バイカラー」。西日にやさしく照らされて。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2607_A7R02741_edit.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2607_A7R02741_edit.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Sunset Reflection</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260708/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Sunset Reflection" /><published>2026-07-08T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2026-07-08T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/hermosa-pier</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260708/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
The setting sun reflects on the wet sand, through the Hermosa Beach Pier.
</p>
<p class="jp">
<span class="title_jp">夕映え</span>
ハーモサ・ビーチ・ピア越しに、沈む夕日が濡れた砂浜に映り込んでいる。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Hermosa Beach" /><category term="Sunset" /><category term="Hermosa Pier" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[The setting sun reflects on the wet sand, through the Hermosa Beach Pier. 夕映え ハーモサ・ビーチ・ピア越しに、沈む夕日が濡れた砂浜に映り込んでいる。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2607_A7R02729.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2607_A7R02729.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Bougainvillea</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260707/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Bougainvillea" /><published>2026-07-07T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2026-07-07T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/bougainvilia</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260707/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
In bloom everywhere around Southern California these days, a branch of bougainvillea in my garden, catching the afternoon sunlight.
</p>
<p class="jp">
<span class="title_jp">ブーゲンビリア</span>
最近、南カリフォルニアの至る所でブーゲンビリアが咲いている。うちの庭でも、ひと枝が午後の日差しを浴びている。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Torrance" /><category term="Flowers" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[In bloom everywhere around Southern California these days, a branch of bougainvillea in my garden, catching the afternoon sunlight. ブーゲンビリア 最近、南カリフォルニアの至る所でブーゲンビリアが咲いている。うちの庭でも、ひと枝が午後の日差しを浴びている。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2607_A7R02622_edit.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2607_A7R02622_edit.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">5th St. Sunset</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260703/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="5th St. Sunset" /><published>2026-07-03T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2026-07-03T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/fifth</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260703/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Setting sun reflects in the water at 5th St. in Hermosa Beach.
</p>
<p class="jp">
<span class="title_jp">5thストリートのサンセット</span>
ハーモサビーチ、5thストリートの水面に映る夕日。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Hermosa Beach" /><category term="Sunset" /><category term="Beach" /><category term="Clouds" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Setting sun reflects in the water at 5th St. in Hermosa Beach. 5thストリートのサンセット ハーモサビーチ、5thストリートの水面に映る夕日。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2607_DSCF0463-HDR.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2607_DSCF0463-HDR.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Foot of Longfellow</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260702/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Foot of Longfellow" /><published>2026-07-02T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2026-07-02T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/longfellow</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260702/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Postcard photo of footprints on the sand at sunset. On the beach at Longfellow St.
</p>
<p class="jp">
