</span>
夕暮れ時の砂浜に刻まれた足跡を写した絵葉書。ロングフェロー通りが浜辺に突き当たる場所にて。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Hermosa Beach" /><category term="Sunset" /><category term="Beach" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Postcard photo of footprints on the sand at sunset. On the beach at Longfellow St. ロングフェローの足元 夕暮れ時の砂浜に刻まれた足跡を写した絵葉書。ロングフェロー通りが浜辺に突き当たる場所にて。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2607_DSCF0327-HDR.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2607_DSCF0327-HDR.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Sandy Beach</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260629/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Sandy Beach" /><published>2026-06-29T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2026-06-29T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/kelp</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260629/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
